title: Ep - 4 -  MTV Road Rules Reunion W/ Jeremy Blossom
description:
Kate speaks with Jeremy Blossom from Road Rules and The Challenge about what transpires behind the scenes of filming, fashion lifestyle photographer Justin Coit provides his thoughts on Real Housewives of Beverly Hills and Orange County, and Kate and her friend Katie discuss an episode of Counting On, the Duggar spin-off series.
